I"D<p>Renee finds herself in an 8th-grade love triangle, Gordon writes short fiction about crime-fighting insects, Sarah confesses to petty crime, and much more. Recorded live at <a href="http://www.thecompanyhouse.ca/">The Company House</a> in Halifax, NS.</p>

